# Root npm lockfile. backend + frontend use pnpm; root has no deps of its
# own (`pnpm-lock.yaml` lives in each subproject). If `npm install` ever
# runs at repo root, this empty lockfile regenerates — ignored so it
# cannot pollute commits.
package-lock.json

